1414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20users%20of%20GLP-1%20medications%20like%20Ozempic%20have%20to%20quit%20taking%20the%20medications.%3Cp%3ECR%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMany%20people%20have%20started%20taking%20Ozempic%2C%20Wegovy%2C%20and%20other%20GLP-1%20drugs%20for%20quick%20weight%20loss.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20some%20end%20up%20having%20to%20quit%20the%20drugs%20due%20to%20other%20medical%20conditions%20or%20trouble%20getting%20more.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat%20puts%20the%20patients%20at%20risk%20of%20gaining%20back%20the%20weight%20that%20they%20lost.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELots%20of%20people%20have%20started%20taking%20weight%20loss%20drugs%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-cracks-down-on-ozempic-content-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOzempic%20and%20Wegovy%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20fewer%20have%20asked%20a%20key%20question%3A%20What%20happens%20if%20they%20need%20to%20stop%20taking%20the%20medications%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20situation%20many%20people%20are%20facing.%20Sometimes%2C%20patients%20have%20to%20stop%20taking%20the%20drugs%20because%20they%20get%20pregnant%20or%20are%20preparing%20for%20surgery%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2024%2F05%2F27%2Fnx-s1-4930028%2Fozempic-wegovy-zepbound-mounjaro-glp1-obesity-weight-loss-regain%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENPR%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20cases%2C%20the%20drugs%20have%20become%20hard%20to%20find.%20One%20patient%20who%20used%20Zepbound%2C%20another%20GLP-1%20drug%2C%20to%20lose%2035%20pounds%20told%20NPR%20that%20he%20had%20to%20start%20using%20a%20rival%20drug%20after%20he%20couldn't%20find%20more%20Zepbound.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20going%20to%20be%20scenarios%2C%20especially%20in%20young%20people%2C%20%5Bwhere%5D%20we%20will%20have%20to%20come%20off%20the%20medicine%2C%20whether%20they%20like%20it%20or%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Rekha%20Kumar%2C%20an%20endocrinologist%20who%20formerly%20served%20as%20medical%20director%20of%20the%20American%20Board%20of%20Obesity%20Medicine%2C%20told%20NPR.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-glp-1-drugs-ozempic-wegovy-mounjaro-effects-future-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGLP-1%20drugs%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy%20have%20been%20touted%20as%20quick%20ways%20to%20lose%20weight%20and%20avoid%20health%20problems%20associated%20with%20obesity%2C%20such%20as%20heart%20problems.%20The%20medications%20rely%20on%20Semaglutide%2C%20an%20active%20ingredient%20that%20reduces%20users'%20appetites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20have%20even%20said%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewidespread%20use%20of%20the%20drugs%20could%20lead%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-economy-faster-growth-ozempic-glp-1-weight-loss-drugs-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeconomic%20growth%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20poor%20health%20imposes%20significant%20economic%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20many%20people%20who%20have%20started%20using%20these%20medicines%20aren't%20obese%20and%20turned%20to%20them%20for%20their%20short-term%20effects.%20If%20patients%20stop%20taking%20the%20medicine%2C%20they%20will%20likely%20gain%20back%20much%20of%20the%20weight%20that%20they%20lost%2C%20especially%20without%20careful%20changes%20to%20their%20diet%20and%20exercise%2C%20NPR%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20study%20released%20earlier%20this%20month%20suggested%20that%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy%20users%20could%20minimize%20that%20weight%20gain%20by%20gradually%20weaning%20themselves%20off%20of%20the%20drugs%20instead%20of%20quitting%20suddenly.%20But%20the%20single%20study%20used%20a%20small%20sample%20size%2C%20indicating%20that%20more%20research%20is%20needed%20to%20confirm%20the%20approach%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-05-11%2Fcoming-off-ozempic-slowly-could-prevent-weight-gain-study-shows%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20drugmakers%20like%20Novo%20Nordisk%2C%20which%20makes%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy%2C%20food%20company%20Nestl%C3%A9%20has%20also%20gotten%20in%20on%20the%20weight%20loss%20frenzy.%20The%20company%20said%20last%20week%2C%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fozempic-wegovy-users-about-to-get-own-frozen-foods-nestle-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVital%20Pursuit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20new%20frozen%20food%20brand%20from%20Nestl%C3%A9%2C%20will%20offer%20small-portioned%20meals%20designed%20for%20GLP-1%20users%20starting%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fozempic-wegovy-users-grapple-with-quitting-weight-loss-drugs-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716836211000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6654ca89239fda2da6cbe819%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fozempic-wegovy-users-grapple-with-quitting-weight-loss-drugs-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Patients%20sometimes%20have%20to%20stop%20using%20GLP-1%20medications%20like%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy%20and%20risk%20regaining%20lost%20weight.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abitter%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Bitter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fozempic-wegovy-users-grapple-with-quitting-weight-loss-drugs-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sunny%20is%20all%20praise%20for%20Sharvari's%20'Taras'%20performance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716836089000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110475145%2Cimgsize-31374.cms%