eter%20atmosphere.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Caribbean%20Princess%20had%20an%20adults-only%20pool%20area%20available%20to%20all%20guests.%20Still%2C%20we%20took%20our%20seclusion%20a%20step%20further%20by%20renting%20a%20cabana%20in%20The%20Sanctuary%2C%20the%20cruise%20line's%20exclusive%20deck%20area%20just%20for%20grown-ups.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%2C%20I%20recharged%20in%20complete%20silence%20by%20reading%20in%20a%20pool%20lounger%20overlooking%20the%20ocean.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHaving%20a%20solo%20dinner%20on%20a%20cruise%20ship%20is%20amazing.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dinner%20menu%20on%20cruise%20ship%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664f551120abc1efe8fcd5f3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere's%20no%20shame%20in%20heading%20to%20dinner%20alone.%3Cp%3ETerri%20Peters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20one%20night%20of%20every%20cruise%2C%20I%20take%20myself%20on%20a%20little%20date%2C%20sending%20my%20husband%20and%20kids%20off%20to%20explore%20the%20ship%20together%20while%20I%20have%20dinner%20on%20my%20own.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20curl%20up%20in%20my%20chair%20with%20a%20good%20book%20and%20eat%20my%20dinner%20peacefully%20while%20I%20allow%20my%20body%20to%20relax%20and%20unwind%20from%20a%20full%20day%20of%20activities.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20no%20one%20at%20my%20table%20to%20chat%20with%2C%20I%20have%20time%20to%20recharge%20and%20quiet%20any%20stresses%20I've%20felt%20throughout%20the%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20fact%2C%20cruising%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20be%20alone%20and%20entertained%20for%20an%20entire%20evening.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Musical%20show%20on%20cruise%20ship%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https