This%20is%20what%20we%20offer%20people%20of%20India'.%20I%20fully%20will%20listen%20to%20him%20and%20take%20him%20seriously%20to%20even%20work%20out%20a%20reply%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Congress%20attack%20currently%20is%20an%20example%20of%20%26quot%3Bfrustration%20gone%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20with%20the%20government%20set%20to%20make%20a%20big%20comeback%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Opposition%20alliance%20are%20already%20working%20on%20the%20next%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20%26quot%3Bstarting%20to%20undertake%20an%20exercise%2C%20as%20it%20were%2C%20to%20deny%20victory%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20Opposition%20%26quot%3Bsore%20and%20bad%20losers%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20minister%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BSeats%20are%20going%20to%20be%20declared%20and%20then%20we%20will%20form%20the%20government.%20But%20they%20would%20want%20to%20raise%20questions%20about%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20EVM%2C%20the%20data%20not%20being%20released.%20You%20know%2C%20the%20tool%20kit%20of%20the%20alliance%20is%20now%20activated%20to%20say%2C%20'Is%20this%20win%20all%20right%3F%20Are%20there%20questions%20about%20this%20win%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20the%20business%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20make%20an%20effective%20Opposition%20campaign%2C%20the%20minister%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20go%20about%20doing%20our%20campaign...%20if%20you%20as%20an%20Opposition%20is%20able%20to%20fight%20this%20election%20effectively%2C%20fight%20it%20out%20and%20if%20you're%20able%20to%20win%2C%20very%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20sense%20she%20is%20getting%2C%20is%20the%20Opposition%20getting%20ready%20to%20question%20the%20victory%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20hoping%20to%20win%20370%20seats%20in%20the%20ongoing%20election%2C%20which%20has%20reached%20the%20last%20stretch.%20The%20party%20has%20given%20its%20NDA%20allies%20a%20target%20of%2030-plus%20seats%2C%20which%20will%20take%20the%20NDA%20score%20to%20400-plus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20phase%20of%20election%20will%20be%20held%20on%20June%201%2C%20the%20counting%20of%20votes%20will%20take%20place%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716830100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fau2lm2mk_nirmala-sitharaman_625x300_27_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsore-and-bad-losers-nirmala-sitharaman-scoffs-at-opposition-alliance-5758960%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20lacks%20the%20vision%20to%20present%20an%20alternative%20solution%20to%20unemployment%20and%20price%20rise%2C%20and%20are%20defensive%20about%20many%20things%2C%20including%20their%20impending%20defeat%20in%20the%20election%2C%20Union%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsore-and-bad-losers-nirmala-sitharaman-scoffs-at-opposition-alliance-5758960%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsore-and-bad-losers-nirmala-sitharaman-scoffs-at-opposition-alliance-5758960%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsore-and-bad-losers-nirmala-sitharaman-scoffs-at-opposition-alliance-5758960%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inside%20photos-videos%20from%20after-party%20of%20SRK's%20KKR%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716830068000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110473598%2Cimgsize-29354.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khan-strikes-a-pose-with-rahmanullah-gurbaz-ananya-panday-shakes-a-leg-with-andre-russell-