n%20registered%20against%20Kataria%20under%20section%20370%20of%20the%20IPC%20at%20the%20Bajghera%20Police%20Station%20Gurugram%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complainants%2C%20Arun%20Kumar%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Fatehpur%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Manish%20Tomar%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Hapur%2C%20said%20that%20they%20were%20unemployed.%20They%20were%20in%20touch%20with%20Kataria%20via%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complainants%20told%20the%20police%20that%20on%20Bobby's%20YouTube%20channel%20MBK%2C%20they%20saw%20an%20advertisement%20about%20abroad-based%20job.%20Following%20this%20they%20called%20Bobby%20Kataria%20on%20on%20his%20WhatsApp.%20Bobby%20called%20them%20to%20meet%20his%20office%20in%20Sector%20109%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20getting%20them%20a%20job%20in%20a%20foreign%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complainant%20then%20met%20Kataria%20in%20his%20office%20on%201%20February%202024%20and%20paid%20Rs%202%2C000%20for%20registration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20this%2C%20on%20the%20request%20of%20Bobby%20Kataria%2C%20on%20February%2013%2C%20Rs%2050%2C000%20was%20transferred%20to%20his%20official%20account%20which%20was%20registered%20in%20the%20name%20of%20MBK%20Global%20Visa%20Private%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20on%20Bobby's%20instruction%20on%20March%2014%2C%20another%20amount%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20was%20transferred%20to%20the%20account%20of%20a%20person%20named%20Ankit%20Shaukeen.%20Kataria%20sent%20the%20tickets%20of%20Vientiane%20(Laos)%20through%20Shaukeen's%20WhatsApp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2028%2C%20as%20per%20the%20instructions%20of%20Bobby%20Kataria%2C%20Kumar%20got%20Rs%2050%2C000%20converted%20into%20USD%20at%20the%20airport%20and%20boarded%20the%20flight%20to%20Vientiane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20lakhs%20of%20rupees%20were%20taken%20from%20his%20friend%20Manish%20Tomar%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20sending%20him%20to%20Singapore%2C%20but%20he%20was%20also%20made%20to%20board%20a%20flight%20to%20Vientiane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20both%20of%20them%20landed%20at%20Vientiane%20airport%2C%20they%20met%20a%20young%20man%20named%20Abhi%2C%20who%20described%20himself%20as%20a%20friend%20of%20Bobby%20Kataria%20and%20a%20Pakistani%20agent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20dropped%20them%20off%20at%20the%20Hotel%20Mican%20Son%20in%20Vientiane%2C%20where%20they%20found%20a%20young%20man%20named%20Ankit%20Shaukeen%20and%20Nitish%20Sharma%20alias%20Rocky.%20They%20took%20the%20victims%20to%20an%20anonymous%20Chinese%20company.%20There%20both%20the%20friends%20were%20severely%20beaten%20and%20their%20passports%20were%20snatched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20commit%20cyber%20fraud%20against%20US%20citizens.%20Both%20of%20them%20were%20threatened%20that%20if%20the%20work%20was%20not%20done%20as%20per%20their%20instructions%20then%20they%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20return%20to%20India%20and%20they%20would%20be%20killed%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAbout%20150%20Indians%20including%20women%20were%20brought%20into%20that%20company%20through%20human%20trafficking%20by%20brokers%20like%20Bobby%20Kataria%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20jobs.%20Somehow%2C%20we%20escaped%20from%20there%20and%20reached%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20and%20came%20back%20to%20India%20and%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20Kataria%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complainant%20told%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716828720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Ffp0k402o_bobby-kataria_625x300_27_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finfluencer-bobby-kataria-arrested-over-human-trafficking-charges-5758651%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Social%20media%20influencer%20Balwant%20Ka