acy%20in%20the%20country%20draws%20to%20a%20close.%20There%20will%20be%20tough%20fights%2C%20some%20even%20in%20the%20BJP%20bastions%20of%20the%20north%2C%20but%20the%20ruling%20party%20will%20gain%20from%20non-BJP%20states%2C%20including%20Telangana%2C%20Odisha%20and%20Bengal%2C%20the%20experts%20said.%20As%20for%20the%20400-seat%20target%2C%20it%20could%20represent%20an%20%26quot%3Baspiration%26quot%3B%20to%20motivate%20people%2C%20ventured%20one%20of%20the%20experts%20at%20NDTV%20Battleground%2C%20anchored%20by%20Editor-in-Chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202024%20election%20has%20bucked%20the%20trend%20of%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20because%20of%20an%20absence%20of%20any%20pro-government%20wave%20or%20public%20anger%20against%20the%20incumbent%2C%20the%20experts%20agreed.%20What%20has%20hit%20the%20country%20instead%20is%20a%20sense%20of%20discontent%2C%20but%20one%20that%20the%20Opposition%20has%20failed%20to%20capitalise%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20journalist%20and%20political%20expert%20Neerja%20Chowdhury%20said%20this%20election%20has%20been%20particularly%20%26quot%3Bcomplex%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdifficult%20to%20decode%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20some%20level%2C%20we%20are%20not%20seeing%20that%20Modi%20wave.%20On%20a%20different%20level%2C%20there%20are%20some%20fence-sitters.%20Modi%20Wave%20cannot%20control%20the%20Opposition%2C%20who%20are%20focussing%20on%20local%20issues.%20The%20Opposition%20is%20giving%20a%20fight%20but%20that%20doesn't%20equal%20victory%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20that%20a%20wave%20is%20seen%20%26quot%3Bafter%20an%20election%26quot%3B%2C%20political%20strategist%20Amitabh%20Tiwari%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BVoting%20is%20an%20emotional%20decision%20--%20hope%20versus%20anger.%20There%20is%20discontent...%20But%20converting%20discontent%20to%20anger%20is%20a%20different%20issue%2C%20one%20that%20needs%20a%20political%20movement%2C%20which%20was%20missing%20from%20the%20Opposition%20list%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMood%20After%20Six%20Phases%20Of%20Election%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20election%20had%20started%20with%20some%20national%20issues%20but%20deviated%20from%20them%20after%20a%20while%2C%20the%20experts%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20started%20its%20campaign%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20national%20issues%2C%20but%20ended%20up%20responding%20to%20the%20Opposition%20agenda%20including%20allegations%20of%20a%20possible%20change%20in%20constitution%2C%20discussions%20of%20which%20had%20flooded%20social%20media%2C%20said%20Sanjay%20Kumar%2C%20psephologist%20from%20CSDS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20leaving%20aside%20the%20noise%20on%20social%20media%2C%20there%20is%20the%20silent%20majority%20that%20makes%20up%20its%20mind%20about%20which%20way%20to%20go%20even%20before%20the%20election%20begins%2C%20the%20panel%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20has%20to%20think%20about%20what%20the%20issue%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20every%20election...%20People%20vote%20for%20a%20bright%20future%20for%20themselves%20and%20their%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tiwari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%20as%20the%20social%20media%20chatter%20is%20concerned%2C%20two%20key%20sections%20are%20missing%20there%20--%20women%20and%20the%20beneficiaries%20of%20welfare%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20the%20two%20sections%20that%20were%20the%20decisive%20factor%20in%20many%20an%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20the%20Opposition%20has%20got%20sidetracked%20and%20misled%20by%20the%20social%20media%20chatter%2C%20Mr%20Tiwari%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20today%2C%20the%20Opposition%20is%20trying%20to%20contain%20the%20BJP%20within%20a%20score%20of%20270%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20is%20a%20defeatist%20attitude%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20hoping%20to%20win%20370%20seats%20in%20the%20ongoing%20election%2C%20which%20has%20reached%20the%20last%20stretch.%20The%20party%20has%20given%20its%20NDA%20allies%20a%20target%20of%2030-plus%20seats%2C%20which%20will%20take%20the%20score%20of%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20to%20400-plus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENon-BJP%20States%20Factor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20the%20view%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20lose%20some%20and%20win%20some%20is%20correct%2C%20Neerja%20Choudhury%20said%20while%20its%20score%20might%20marginally%20drop%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20north%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20party%20will%20make%20up%20for%20it%20in%20the%20non-BJP%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKey%20among%20them%20will%20be%20Odisha%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20they%20are%20expected%20to%20get%20more%20seats%20owing%20to%20their%20alliance%20with%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20and%20Telangana%2C%20where%20the%20Congress%20has%20decimated%20K%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao's%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnSanjay%20Kumar%20agreed%2C%20saying%20while%20the%20BJP%20might%20lose%20a%20few%20seats%2C%20it%20will%20not%20be%20enough%20to%20cause%20a%20major%20difference%2C%20especially%20with%20their%20gains%20from%20non-BJP%20states.%20His%20analogy%20for%20this%20was%20cricket%20--%20at%20times%20when%20the%20opening%20batsmen%20end%20up%20with%20a%20less-than-stellar%20performance%2C%20the%20middle%20order%20makes%20up%20for%20it%2C%20he%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20states%20that%20would%20make%20a%20material%20difference%20to%20the%20BJP%20score%20would%20be%20Bengal%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20said%20Sandeep%20Shastri%2C%20psephologist%20from%20CSDS.%20It%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20the%20allies%20would%20drag%20the%20BJP%20down%20or%20the%20BJP%20would%20be%20able%20to%20carry%20them%20along%2C%20he%20said.%20In%20Bengal%2C%20the%20outcome%20differs%20depending%20on%20who%20one%20is%20speaking%20to%2C%20the%20experts%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20phase%20of%20election%20will%20be%20held%20on%20June%201%2C%20the%20counting%20of%20votes%20will%20take%20place%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716827580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fho2ok4u8_ndtv-battleground_625x300_27_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftough-fight-no-sweep-victory-at-a-cost-ndtv-scans-battleground-5758314%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20public%20mood%20is%20tough%20to%20read%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20Election%20and%20while%20the%20BJP%20will%20get%20majority%2C%20one%20can%20expect%20the%20unexpected%3A%20This%20is%20what%20a%20group%20of%20experts%20at%20NDTV%20concluded%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftough-fight-no-sweep-victory-at-a-cost-ndtv-scans-battleground-5758314%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftough-fight-no-sweep-victory-at-a-cost-ndtv-scans-battleground-5758314%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftough-fight-no-sweep-victory-at-a-cost-ndtv-scans-battleground-5758314%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20to%20build%20Central%20Asia's%20first%20nuclear%20power%20plant%20in%20Uzbekistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716827435000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110473270%2Cimgsize-842434.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Frussia-to-build-central-asias-first-nuclear-power-plant-in-uzbekistan%2Farticleshow%2F110472948.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110472948.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERussia%20will%20build%20Central%20Asia's%20first%20nuclear%20power%20plant%2C%20a%20%24500%20milli