%20corruption%20rackets%20and%20called%20out%20the%20'Khan%20Market%20gang'%20for%20scripting%20a%20fake%20narrative%20to%20save%20them%20from%20the%20grip%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%2C%20speaking%20exclusively%20to%20IANS%2C%20said%20that%2C%20unlike%20earlier%20regimes%2C%20not%20the%20small%20players%20but%20big%20fish%20and%20perpetrators%20are%20being%20brought%20to%20book%20under%20his%20watch%20and%20this%20was%20breaking%20the%20backs%20of%20their%20masters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20same%20people%20who%20earlier%20cried%20foul%20over%20no%20action%20on%20big%20players%20have%20started%20crying%20hoarse%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20expressed%20dismay%20over%20a%20recent%20trend%2C%20which%20he%20said%2C%20was%20the%20glorification%20of%20the%20corrupt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarlier%2C%20people%20used%20to%20stay%20100%20steps%20away%20from%20the%20convicted%20or%20even%20those%20with%20any%20corruption%20taint%20but%20today%20there%20is%20a%20tendency%20to%20support%20and%20rally%20behind%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%2C%20further%20speaking%20to%20IANS%2C%20explained%20how%20his%20government%20questioned%20in%202019%20for%20going%20slow%20on%20the%20corrupt%20and%20shady%20practices%2C%20has%20ensured%20the%20prosecution%20of%20big%20fish%20and%20racketeers%20and%20also%20stated%20that%20this%20has%20triggered%20a%20wave%20of%20protests%20and%20backlash%20from%20certain%20sections%20of%20Opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20same%20people%20who%20demanded%20that%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20be%20put%20behind%20bars%20are%20crying%20hoarse%20over%20action%20against%20corruption%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20explained%20that%20the%20action%20against%20the%20corrupt%20and%20the%20dishonest%20was%20based%20on%20facts%20and%20evidence%2C%20and%20not%20on%20perception.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3