20rivals.%20The%20snooping%20operation%20was%20supposed%20to%20create%20a%20dossier%20to%20manage%20possible%20threats%3B%20in%20a%20twist%2C%20Mr%20Rao's%20BRS%20was%20thumped%20by%20the%20Congress%20anyway%2C%20winning%20only%2039%20(down%20from%2088%20in%202018)%20of%20the%20state's%20119%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArrested%20on%20March%2029%20from%20his%20home%20in%20Hyderabad's%20Banjara%20Hills%2C%20Mr%20Rao%20has%20reportedly%20admitted%20to%20former%20colleagues%20that%20he%20was%20part%20of%20this%20alleged%20illegal%20enterprise%2C%20which%20may%20have%20snooped%20on%20a%20prominent%20people%2C%20including%20media%20personalities%20Narendra%20Choudary%20of%20NTV%20and%20Vemuri%20Radhakrishna%20of%20ABN%2C%20retired%20police%20officer%20RS%20Praveen%20Kumar%2C%20sitting%20Warangal%20MP%20Kadiyam%20Srihari%2C%20and%20former%20BRS%20minister%20Patnam%20Mahender%20Reddy%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Sunita%20Reddy.%20Patnam%20Mahender%20Reddy%20has%20now%20shifted%20to%20the%20Congress%20and%20was%20the%20party's%20candidate%20for%20the%20Malkajgiri%20seat%20in%20the%202024%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20party%20leaders%20-%20such%20as%20the%20Congress'%20Saritha%20Thirupathaiah%2C%20who%20contested%20and%20lost%20the%20Gadwal%20Assembly%20seat%20last%20year%20to%20the%20BRS'%20BK%20Mohan%20Reddy%20-%20were%20reportedly%20also%20targeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERadhakrishna%20Rao%20reportedly%20also%20claimed%20T%20Prabhakar%20Rao%2C%20then%20chief%20of%20the%20Special%20Intelligence%20Bureau%2C%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20op%2C%20which%20gathered%20data%20on%20anyone%20who%20seemed%20to%20be%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20then-ruling%20BRS.%20Once%20an%20individual%20was%20flagged%2C%20the%20Intelligence%20Bureau's%20deputy%20chief%2C%20Praneeth%20Kumar%2C%20was%20reportedly%20tasked%20with%20creating%20profiles%20to%20manage%20possible%20'threats'%20to%20the%20BRS'%20hold%20on%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alleged%20snooping%20did%20not%20only%20target%20political%20leaders%20or%20public%20figures.%20Mr%20Rao%20said%20businesspersons%20in%20the%20real%20estate%20and%20construction%20industries%20were%20also%20tracked%20to%20establish%20their%20affiliations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20rumours%20of%20the%20snooping%20spread%2C%20bureaucrats%2C%20members%20of%20judiciary%2C%20and%20political%20figures%20avoided%20direct%20phone%20calls%20and%2C%20instead%2C%20used%20encrypted%20messaging%20services%20like%20WhatsApp%20and%20Signal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ft-prabhakar-rao-telangana-phone-tapping-case-ex-intel-bureau-chief-named-accused-no-1-in-telangana-phone-tapping-row-5307258%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEx-Intel%20Bureau%20Chief%20Is%20Accused%20No%201%20In%20Phone-Tapping%20Row%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Prabhakar%20Rao%20and%20his%20group%20allegedly%20tracked%20communications%20over%20internet%20calls%20by%20acquiring%20and%20examining%20Internet%20Protocol%20Data%20Records%20(IPDRs).%20This%20has%20now%20triggered%20fresh%20moral%20and%20legal%20concerns%20over%20the%20use%20of%20public%20resources%20and%20technology%20for%20personal%20or%20political%20gain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20particularly%20unsettling%20aspect%20concerned%20iNews%20journalist%20Sravan%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mr%20Rao%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20spoke%20directly%20T%20Prabhakar%20Rao%20during%20the%20state%20election%20in%20October%20and%20November%20last%20year%3B%20this%20meeting%20is%20said%20to%20have%20been%20at%20the%20request%20of%20the%20T%20Harish%20Rao%2C%20a%20BRS%20leader%20who%20was%20then%20a%20member%20of%20the%20cabinet%C2%A0and%20is%20nephew%20of%20ex-Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInformation%20about%20opposition%20leaders%20and%20their%20financial%20backers%20was%20reportedly%20sent%20to%20the%20Intelligence%20Bureau%20via%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%20and%20this%20was%20used%20to%20target%20rivals%20during%20cash%20seizure%20ops.%20Mr%20Kumar%20reportedly%20also%20helped%20Praneeth%20Kumar%20wage%20trolling%20campaigns%20against%20the%20BRS'%20detractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERadhakrishna%20Rao%20made%20other%20startling%20claims%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsouth%2Ftelangana-phone-tapping-case-senior-cop-radhakrishna-rao-arrested-in-telangana-phone-tap-row-makes-sensational-claims-5353036%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESenior%20Cop%20Arrested%20In%20Telangana%20Phone%20Tap%20Row%20Makes%20Big%20Claim%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20alleged%20cash%20had%20been%20moved%20in%20official%20vehicles%20in%20the%202018%20and%202023%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20and%20gave%20the%20Munugode%20by-poll%20as%20an%20example.%20He%20claimed%20Rs%203.5%20crore%20had%20been%20confiscated%20from%20people%20linked%20to%20Komatireddy%20Raj%20Gopal%20Reddy%2C%20who%20contested%20the%20by-poll%20on%20a%20BJP%20ticket.%20He%20lost%20to%20the%20BRS'%20KP%20Reddy%20but%20then%20jumped%20to%20the%20Congress%20for%20the%202023%20election%20and%20won%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Telangana%20phone-tapping%20case%20involves%20the%20alleged%20gathering%20of%20electronic%20data%20not%20just%20for%20political%20intelligence%2C%20but%20to%20blackmail%20leaders%2C%20and%20even%20private%20companies%20and%20Tollywood%20celebrities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20N%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%20told%20NDTV%20all%20this%20happened%20with%20the%20knowledge%20of%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20previous%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20government.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20before%20they%20(BRS)%20leaders%20come%20under%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Reddy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2F