nt%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20(BCCI)%20in%20India%20has%20started%20to%20look%20out%20for%20a%20new%20head%20coach%20for%20the%20men's%20Indian%20cricket%20team.%20The%20tenure%20of%20Rahul%20Dravid%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20the%20head%20coach%20of%20the%20Rohit%20Sharma-led%20side%2C%20is%20going%20to%20end%20with%20the%20conclusion%20of%20India's%20campaign%20at%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024.%20The%20final%20match%20of%20the%20event%20will%20take%20place%20on%20June%2029.%20BCCI%20has%20already%20started%20inviting%20applications%20for%20the%20job%20with%20the%20deadline%20being%20May%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20former%20India%20opener%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20front%20runner%20for%20the%20role%20among%20the%20names%20that%20are%20surfacing.%20Of%20latest%2C%20former%20England%20spinner%20Graeme%20Swann%20has%20also%20shown%20his%20interest%20in%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20India%20asked%20me%20to%20become%20their%20coach%2C%20I'd%20do%20it%20in%20a%20heartbeat!%20I%20love%20this%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Swann%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF77iGcdVVUA%3Fsi%3Dhvq1NuZDrArDgB3q%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESports%20Tak%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAndy%20was%20an%20incredible%20coach%20for%20England%20when%20I%20played.%20He%20took%20us%20to%20no.1%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20was%20the%20best%20coach%20I've%20played%20under.%20India%20would%20be%20lucky%20to%20have%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Swann%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia...%20you've%20got%20such%20a%20strong%20squad%2C%20such%20highly%20talented%20players%2C%20that%20whoever%20gets%20the%20job...%20it%20will%20be%20the%20biggest%20coaching%20job%20in%20the%20world%20of%20cricket%20these%20days.%20Whoever%20gets%20it%2C%20hope%20they%20can%20bringing%20success%20because%20they%20are%20really%20under%20the%20microscope%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeams%20like%20Pakistan%2C%20England%20and%20South%20Africa%20have%20adopted%20split%20coaching%20but%20Swann%20had%20earlier%20suggested%20that%20the%20Indian%20team%20doesn't%20need%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20England%2C%20we%20have%20three%20teams%20that%20go%20all%20around%20the%20world%20cause%20our%20summer%20is%20in%20a%20different%20time%2C%20that's%20one%20of%20the%20main%20reasons%20that%20split%20coaches%20in%20England.%20You%20don't%20need%20it%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Swann%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20good%20coach%20is%20a%20good%20coach%2C%20he's%20the%20right%20man%20for%20all%20three%20forms%20so%20be%20it.%20If%20the%20guy%20is%20specialist%20in%20white%20ball%20cricket%20and%20he's%20available%20then%20you%20can%20use%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716821160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F4en448j8_indian-cricket-team_625x300_02_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fid-do-it-in-a-heartbeat-england-great-throws-hat-in-india-head-coach-race-5744906%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20(BCCI)%20in%20India%20has%20started%20to%20look%20out%20for%20a%20new%20head%20coach%20for%20the%20men's%20team.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fid-do-it-in-a-heartbeat-england-great-throws-hat-in-india-head-coach-race-5744906%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fid-do-it-in-a-heartbeat-england-great-throws-hat-in-india-head-coach-race-5744906%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fid-do-it-in-a-heartbeat-england-great-throws-hat-in-india-head-coach-race-5744906%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nalco%20Q4%20results%3A%20PAT%20rises%20two-fold%20to%20Rs%20996.7%20cr%20on%20lower%20expenses%22%2C%22conte