mote%20disaster%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcerns%20about%20further%20mudslides%20triggered%20by%20relentless%20rains%20have%20intensified%2C%20adding%20another%20layer%20of%20complexity%20to%20the%20rescue%20operation.%20Authorities%20anticipate%20the%20search%20efforts%20to%20continue%20for%20days%2C%20with%20the%20true%20scope%20of%20the%20tragedy%20likely%20to%20evolve%20as%20rescue%20teams%20gain%20access.%20Though%20the%20Yandams'%20survival%20offers%20a%20much-needed%20reprieve%2C%20the%20overall%20situation%20in%20Enga%20province%20remains%20critically%20serious.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BWe%20thank%20God%20for%20saving%20our%20lives%20at%20that%20moment.%20We%20were%20certain%20that%20we%20were%20going%20to%20die%20but%20the%20big%20rocks%20didn't%20crush%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Jacklyn%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20hard%20to%20explain%20as%20we%20got%20trapped%20for%20nearly%20eight%20hours%2C%20then%20got%20rescued.%20We%20believe%20we%20were%20saved%20for%20a%20purpose.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20landslide%20occurred%20in%20the%20mountainous%20Enga%20region%20in%20northern%20Papua%20New%20Guinea%20on%20Friday%20last%20week%20and%20the%20latest%20figure%20is%20a%20sharp%20rise%20from%20earlier%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20disaster%20occurred%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20confirmed%20that%20as%20many%20as%20100%20people%20may%20have%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20was%20later%20revised%20up%20to%20670%2C%20according%20to%20estimates%20from%20the%20Chief%20of%20Mission%20for%20the%20International%20Organisation%20for%20Migration%20(IOM)%20in%20the%20country%2C%20CNN%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20may%20now%20be%20a%20major%20underestimate%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20projection%20from%20Papua%20New%20Guinea's%20disaster%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20landslide%20buried%20more%20than%202000%20people%20alive%2C%20caused%20major%20destruction%20to%20buildings%2C%20and%20food%20gardens%20and%20caused%20major%20impact%20on%20the%20economic%20lifeline%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Lusete%20Laso%20Mana%2C%20Acting%20Director%20of%20the%20National%20Disaster%20Centre%2C%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20UN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20remains%20unstable%20as%20the%20landslip%20continues%20to%20shift%20slowly%2C%20posing%20ongoing%20danger%20to%20both%20rescue%20teams%20and%20survivors%20alike%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20main%20highway%20to%20the%20area%20had%20been%20completely%20blocked%20by%20the%20landslide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Papua%20New%20Guinea%20is%20home%20to%20around%2010%20million%20people.%20Its%20vast%20mountainous%20terrain%20and%20lack%20of%20roads%20have%20made%20it%20difficult%20to%20access%20the%20affected%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716819900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fljdsqiv_papua-new-guinea_625x300_27_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fcouple-cheats-death-in-papua-new-guinea-landslide-that-killed-2-000-people-5757937%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20government%20estimates%20over%202%2C000%20people%20may%20be%20buried%20under%20the%20debris%2C%20only%20six%20bodies%20have%20been%20recovered.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fcouple-cheats-death-in-papua-new-guinea-landslide-that-killed-2-000-people-5757937%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fcouple-cheats-death-in-papua-new-guinea-landslide-that-killed-2-000-people-5757937%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fcouple-cheats-death-in-papua-new-guinea-landslide-that-killed-2-000-people-5757937%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22North%20Korea's%20latest%20attempt%20to%20launch%20a%20satellite%20fails%20after%20rocket%