ra%20Modi's%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20been%20going%20on%20for%20two-and-a-half%20years%20(referring%20to%20the%20Rajkot%20gaming%20zone).%20Are%20we%20to%20assume%20you%20turned%20a%20blind%20eye%3F%20What%20do%20you%20and%20your%20followers%20do%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20thundered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajkot%20gaming%20zone%2C%20it%20has%20emerged%2C%20was%20granted%20a%20license%20by%20local%20cops%20in%20November%20last%20year%2C%20which%20was%20renewed%20to%20December%2031%2C%202024%2C%20Mr%20Bhargava%20had%20admitted%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyou-turned-a-blind-eye-high-court-slams-municipal-body-over-rajkot-fire-5754728%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20Trust%20Gujarat%20Government%26quot%3B%3A%20High%20Court%20On%20Rajkot%20Fire%20Lapses%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20criticised%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHave%20you%20gone%20blind%3F%20Did%20you%20fall%20asleep%3F%20Now%20we%20do%20not%20trust%20the%20local%20system%20and%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20raged%20when%20told%20fire%20safety%20certification%20hearings%20have%20been%20unresolved%20for%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETold%20about%20three%20establishments%20in%20Ahmedabad%20that%20do%20not%20follow%20fire%20safety%20regulations%2C%20and%20that%20the%20rules%20say%20a%20gaming%20zone%20is%20not%20allowed%20without%20a%20NOC%20from%20the%20city's%20fire%20department%2C%20an%20irate%20High%20Court%20shot%20back%2C%20%26quot%3BThen%20this%20rule%20was%20not%20followed%20in%20Rajkot...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajkot-game-zone-fire-gujarat-high-court-cant-run-game-zone-at-cost-of-small-children-being-killed-high-court-5755909%5C%22%20target%3