Cn%3Cp%3ESandeep%E2%80%99s%20dream%20is%20to%20create%20an%20Indian%20brand%20with%20footprints%20across%20the%20world.%20His%20biggest%20validation%2C%20he%20says%2C%20eventually%20came%20from%20his%20father%20who%20praised%20Sandeep%20for%20his%20exceptional%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20dreams%20came%20true%20through%20Pizza%20Galleria.%20From%20drawing%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%209%2C000%20per%20month%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20able%20to%20buy%20my%20own%20house%20and%20car.%20What%20matters%20most%20to%20me%20is%20my%20family%E2%80%99s%20praise%2C%20which%20is%20something%20money%20can%E2%80%99t%20buy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Sandeep%20had%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303449%2Fmumbai-duo-quit-job-to-make-authentic-neapolitan-pizza-earn-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20bite%20of%20pizza%20in%202014%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20little%20did%20he%20know%20that%20he%20would%20be%20selling%20over%207%20lakh%20pizzas%20a%20month%20a%20decade%20later!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWork%20hard%20to%20fulfil%20your%20dreams.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20stop%20yourself%20from%20achieving%20big%20dreams%20because%20you%E2%80%99re%20from%20a%20small%20town.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20best%20time%20to%20start%20a%20business.%20Start%20small%3B%20even%20food%20carts%20have%20turned%20into%20massive%20businesses.%20Live%20your%20life%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20it%20becomes%20an%20example%20for%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Sandeep%20Jangra%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716817228000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsandeep-1716813220.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351202%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Inspired%20by%20his%20first%20bite%20of%20pizza%2C%20Sandeep%20Jangra%20o