s%2C%20including%20updates%20to%20Azure%20and%20Copilot%2C%20along%20with%20groundbreaking%20innovations%20from%20Microsoft%20partners%20like%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nadella%20shared%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20January%202023%2C%20I%20met%20a%20rural%20Indian%20farmer%20who%20used%20GPT-3.5%2C%20in%20his%20own%20voice%2C%20to%20understand%20government%20farm%20subsidies%20he'd%20heard%20about%20on%20television.%20It%20was%20a%20powerful%20moment%20for%20me.%20It%20illustrated%20the%20incredible%20impact%20of%20a%20cutting-edge%20model%20developed%20on%20the%20West%20Coast%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20now%20being%20used%20to%20directly%20improve%20the%20life%20of%20a%20rural%20farmer%20in%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20during%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum's%20annual%20meeting%20at%20Davos%2C%20Mr%20Nadella%20in%20conversation%20with%20Klaus%20Schwab%2C%20founder%20and%20executive%20chairman%20of%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20(WEF)%2C%20cited%20the%20example%20of%20the%20Indian%20farmer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nadella%20shared%20that%20the%20farmer%20was%20trying%20to%20access%20some%20government%20programme.%20%26quot%3BHe%20expressed%20a%20complex%20need%20in%20one%20of%20the%20local%20languages.%20This%20got%20translated%20and%20interpreted%20by%20a%20bot%20and%20a%20response%20came%20back%20saying%20go%20to%20a%20portal%20and%20here%20is%20how%20you%20will%20access%20the%20programme%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nadella%20revealed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Microsoft%20CEO%20further%20shared%20that%20the%20farmer%20was%20initially%20hesitant%20to%20use%20the%20programme%20and%20asked%20the%20bot%20to%20do%20it%20on%20his%20behalf.%20%26quot%3BAnd%2C%20it%20completed%20it%20and%20the%20reason%20why%20it%20was%20able%20to%20complete%20it%20was%20that%20the%20developer%20building%20it%20had%20taken%20GPT%20%5BGeneral%20Purpose%20Technology%5D%20and%20trained%20it%20over%20all%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India%20documents%20and%20then%20scaffolded%20it%20with%20the%20speech%20recognition%20software%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nadella%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Build%202024%20conference%2C%20Microsoft%20made%20a%20splash%20in%20the%20AI%20world%20with%20two%20key%20announcements.%20First%2C%20developers%20can%20now%20access%20OpenAI's%20most%20powerful%20model%20yet%2C%20GPT-40.%20This%20cutting-edge%20tool%20promises%20to%20revolutionize%20AI%20capabilities.%20%C2%A0Second%2C%20Microsoft%20introduced%20Phi-3-Vision%2C%20a%20new%20Small%20Language%20Model%20(SLM)%20with%20the%20remarkable%20ability%20to%20read%20and%20understand%20images.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20groundbreaking%20tools%20will%20be%20available%20on%20Microsoft's%20Azure%20AI%20Studio%2C%20a%20one-stop%20shop%20for%20developers%20to%20leverage%20these%20advancements%20and%20push%20the%20boundaries%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20didn't%20stop%20there.%20They%20also%20unveiled%20powerful%20new%20virtual%20machines%20specifically%20designed%20for%20handling%20AI%20workloads%20with%20unmatched%20efficiency.%20Significantly%2C%20they%20became%20the%20first%20cloud%20provider%20to%20integrate%20AMD's%20cutting-edge%20MI300X%20AI%20accelerator%20chip.%20This%20integration%20strengthens%20the%20Azure%20ND%20MI300X%20v5%20virtual%20machine%20series%2C%20making%20it%20a%20powerhouse%20for%20running%20complex%20AI%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716813420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Ft5kdub58_satya-nadella_625x300_08_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpowerful-moment-satya-nadella-reveals-how-gpt-3-5-helped-an-indian-farmer-5757176%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mr%20Nadella%20shared%20that%20the%20farmer%20was%20trying%20to%20access%20some%20government%20programme.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpowerful-moment-satya-nadella-reveals-how