s%20for%20the%20%3Cem%3Eidli%3C%2Fem%3E%20batter%20and%20%3Cem%3Esambhar%3C%2Fem%3E.%20While%20the%20ration%20items%20she%20gets%20aren%E2%80%99t%20sufficient%20for%20the%20quantity%20she%20makes%2C%20regular%20customers%20and%20well-wishers%20help%20her%20with%20their%20ration%20rice.%20This%20goodwill%20and%20her%20benevolent%20heart%20are%20the%20major%20reasons%20for%20her%20pricing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20started%2C%203%20paise%20for%20one%20%3Cem%3Eidli%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20less%20than%20other%20hotels%2C%20but%20it%20helped%20everyone%20afford%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20principle%20is%20the%20reason%20that%20has%20prevented%20her%20from%20increasing%20the%20price%20even%20today%2C%20even%20as%20nearby%20hotels%20charge%20at%20least%20Rs%2010%20per%20idli.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20doing%20this%20for%20profit%2C%20all%20I%20want%20is%20the%20love%20of%20my%20customers.%20That%20keeps%20me%20going.%20Will%20school%20children%20be%20able%20to%20afford%20more%3F%20Everyone%20is%20struggling%20for%20money%2C%20and%20this%20is%20my%20way%20of%20helping%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2084-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20source%20of%20inspiration%20for%20her%20service%20are%20the%20people%20who%20do%20%3Cem%3Eannadanam%20%3C%2Fem%3E(food%20donation).%20When%20they%20can%20provide%20food%20and%20clothes%20to%20so%20many%2C%20why%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20she%20do%20something%20in%20her%20capacity%2C%20she%20thought%20to%20herself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20not%20increase%20it%20to%20enable%20a%20better%20life%20for%20herself%3F%20%E2%80%9CLet%20it%20be.%20Why%20should%20an%20old%20lady%20be%20greedy%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20firmly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20love%20keeps%20her%20customers%20coming%20back.%20Saravanan%2C%20a%20regular%20customer%2C%20shares%20that%20he%20has%20been%20eating%20at%20Dhanam%20%3Cem%3EPaati%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20shop%20since%20he%20was%20a%20child