title%22%3A%22The%20%E2%80%98MBA%20Sarpanch%E2%80%99%20Who%20Kept%20All%20Her%20Promises%20%26amp%3B%20Brought%20Water%2C%20Roads%20%26amp%3B%20Education%20to%20a%20Village%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20lies%20a%20road%20in%20the%20main%20bazaar%20%3Cem%3Echowk%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20Soda%20village%20of%20Rajasthan.%20At%20first%20glance%2C%20it%20may%20seem%20like%20an%20ordinary%20village%20street%2C%20but%20the%20locals%20see%20it%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20progress.%20As%20I%20get%20on%20a%20call%20with%20Ladu%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20farmer%20in%20the%20area%2C%20the%20steady%20sound%20of%20trucks%2C%20cars%2C%20bullock%20carts%2C%20buses%2C%20and%20bicycles%20ploughing%20through%20the%20street%20eclipse%20most%20of%20his%20words.%20He%20shouts%20over%20the%20din%2C%20%E2%80%9CNow%20trucks%20can%20drive%20on%20this%20road!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELadu%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20goes%20on%20to%20explain%20why%20this%20is%20a%20miracle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20even%20two%20bicycles%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20pass%20simultaneously.%20What%20else%20can%20you%20expect%20from%20a%20two-foot-wide%20road%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asks.%20I%20agree.%20So%2C%20naturally%2C%20watching%20the%20path%20accommodating%20trucks%20and%20lorries%20is%20amusing%20for%20the%20villagers.%20The%20farmer%20is%20quick%20to%20hail%20his%20ex-%3Cem%3Esarpanch%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20decision-maker%20elected%20by%20the%20village)%20Chhavi%20Rajawat%20for%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F85603%2Fwomen-sarpanches-transforming-inspiring-villages%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ephenomenal%20work%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20stresses%20though%20that%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20transformation%20she%20has%20brought%20about.%20%E2%80%9COur%20village%20has%20water%20thanks%20to%20her.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Rajawat%20took%20over%20as%20%3Cem%3Esarpanch%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%202010%20%E2%80%94%20at%20the%20time%20making%20headlines%20for%20being%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20%3Cem%3Esarpanch%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20an%20MBA%20degree%20%E2%80%94%20the%20village%20was%20experiencing%20one%20of%20its%20worst%20droughts.%20%E2%80%9CMadam%20ensured%20a%20pipeline%20in%20every%20house%20and%20water%20in%20every%20pond%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ladu%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHome%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20place%20where%20he%20has%20been%20witnessing%20the%20results%20of%20Rajawat%E2%80%99s%20work.%20His%20fields%20too%20have%20benefited.%20Promising%20to%20send%20me%20pictures%20of%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313207%2Faravinthan-coimbatore-organic-farm-seed-bank-preserves-rare-varieties-vegetables-pulses%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethriving%20pulses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20farmer%20credits%20the%20steady%20supply%20of%20water%20for%20this.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%20my%20fields%20would%20dry%20up%20completely.%20But%20not%20anymore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20suffices%20to%20say%20that%20in%20the%20two%20terms%20that%20Rajawat%20headed%20the%20village%20as%20%3Cem%3Esarpanch%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%202010-15%20and%202015-20%2C%20she%20shaped%2C%20both%2C%20policies%20and%20dreams.%20As%20she%20points%20out%2C%20the%20victory%20is%20personal.%20After%20all%2C%20this%20is%20her%20native%20village.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20was%20chasing%20corporate%20dreams%20%E2%80%94%20Rajawat%20worked%20for%20a%20slew%20of%20multinational%20companies%20after%20completing%20her%20MBA%20degree%20%E2%80%94%20one%20question%20continued%20to%20baffle%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20government%20funding%20for%20rural%20development%20increasing%20over%20the%20years%2C%20why%20were%20villages%20not%20progressing%3F%20Why%20was%20development%20in%20retreat%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConversations%20with%20the%20villagers%20led%20her%20to%20the%20answer.%20%E2%80%9CI%20began%20to%20understand%20that%20responsibility%20and%20ownership%20were%20slowly%20regressing%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dindian%2Bvillages%2Bthe%2Bbetter%2Bindia%26rlz%3D1C1YTUH_enIN1048IN1048%26oq%3Dindian%2Bvillages%2Bthe%2Bbetter%2Bindia%26gs_lcrp%3DEgZjaHJvbWUyBggAEEUYOTIJCAEQIRgKGKABMgkIAhAhGAoYoAHSAQg0OTcyajBqNKgCALACAA%26sourceid%3Dchrome%26ie%3DUTF-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erural%20landscapes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20469px)%20100vw%2C%20469px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSarpanch-Chhavi-with-the-goat_11zon-1715862357.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22469%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ex-Sarpanch%20Chhavi%20Rajawat%20has%20transformed%20the%20village%20of%20Soda%20into%20a%20space%20for%20development%2C%20education%20and%20change%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSarpanch-Chhavi-with-the-goat_11zon-1715862357.jpg%20469w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSarpanch-Chhavi-with-the-goat_11zon-1715862357-226x300.jpg%20226w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSarpanch-Chhavi-with-the-goat_11zon-1715862357-150x199.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350275%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22623%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEx-Sarpanch%20Chhavi%20Rajawat%20has%20transformed%20the%20village%20of%20Soda%20into%20a%20space%20for%20development%2C%20education%20and%20change%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Chhavi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajawat%E2%80%99s%20stint%20as%20%3Cem%3Esarpanch%3C%2Fem%3E%20witnessed%20800%20households%20getting%20pipelines%2C%20around%20800%20homes%20getting%20toilets%2C%20numerous%20ponds%20being%20revived%2C%20and%20100%20roads%20being%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20when%20the%20villagers%20assumed%20the%20spate%20of%20development%20had%20reached%20its%20peak%2C%20Rajawat%20revived%20a%20defunct%20college%20and%20is%20already%20planning%20for%20a%20digital%20literacy%20centre.%20%E2%80%9CMiles%20to%20go%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20emphasises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKnowledge%20does%20not%20discriminate%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20Monday%20morning%20when%20I%20call%20Geeta%20(44).%20Her%20delayed%20response%2C%20as%20she%20explains%2C%20is%20because%20she%20is%20busy%20sketching%20out%20a%20curriculum%20for%20her%20Class%205%20students.%20It%E2%80%99s%20been%20a%20year%20since%20Geeta%20has%20been%20working%20at%20this%20school.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20the%20happiest%20I%20have%20ever%20been%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%20After%20being%20unemployed%20for%20years%2C%20she%20is%20relieved%20to%20have%20a%20well-paying%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Class%2012%2C%20Geeta%20quit%20her%20studies%20for%20five%20years.%20Her%20father%E2%80%99s%20untimely%20demise%20and%20her%20in-laws%E2%80%99%20unsupportive%20behaviour%20were%20the%20reasons.%20But%2C%20it%20was%20a%20friend%20who%20stepped%20in%20and%20motivated%20Geeta%20to%20take%20up%20studying%20once%20again%3B%20transferring%20Rs%203%2C000%20into%20her%20bank%20account%20and%20asking%20her%20to%20channel%20the%20money%20towards%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348078%2Fdelhi-constable-than-singh-ki-pathshala-teaches-underprivileged-children-for-free%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeducation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20at%20a%20construction%20site%20in%20Jaipur%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Geeta%20was%20forced%20to%20return%20to%20Soda%20in%202020.%20The%20dearth%20of%20work%20during%20the%20COVID%20lockdown%20made%20it%20impossible%20for%20her%20to%20continue.%20When%20she%20reached%20the%20village%2C%20news%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98new%E2%80%99%20college%20taking%20in%20applicants%20reached%20her.%20One%20conversation%20with%20Rajawat%20later%2C%20Geeta%20was%20convinced%20this%20was%20the%20place%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChhavi%20ma%E2%80%99am%20encouraged%20me%20to%20pursue%20my%20D%20El%20Ed%20(Diploma%20in%20Elementary%20Education).%20Everyone%20around%20me%20was%20keen%20to%20see%20me%20study.%20I%20began%20noticing%20how%20the%20village%20mindset%20had%20evolved.%E2%80%9D%20Geeta%20went%20on%20to%20complete%20the%20two-year%20course%20and%20secured%20a%20job%20at%20the%20village%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338824%2Fmuskaan-dreams-abhishek-dubey-introduces-technology-in-rural-school-education-digital-literacy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimparting%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%2010-year-olds%20is%20her%20first%20priority%2C%20another%20goal%20is%20to%20dispel%20stereotypes%20that%20force%20women%20to%20sacrifice%20their%20dreams.%20Currently%2C%20there%20are%20550%20students%20at%20the%20college.%20They%20are%20engaged%20in%20one%20of%20the%20three%20courses%20offered%20here%3A%20BEd%20(Bachelor%20of%20Education)%2C%20a%20D%20El%20Ed%20(Diploma%20in%20Elementary%20Education)%2C%20and%20a%20BA%20(Bachelor%20of%20Arts)%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201288px)%20100vw%2C%201288px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-19-at-5.34.52-PM-1-1715862133.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221288%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chhavi%20Rajwat%20is%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20affairs%20at%20the%20girls'%20college%20in%20Soda%20village%20in%20Rajasthan%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsAp